tags.name: Traeth Penbryn Beach
tags.note: Dogs are prohibited from the beach to the South of the River Hoffnant. No restrictions to the North of the River. Signage not particularly clear, but restrictions confirmed with the National Trust.

tags.name: Llangrannog Beach
tags.note: Dogs are banned to the West of the stream on the beach from 1st May to 30th September. No restrictions to the East of the stream or Cilborth Beach.

tags.name: Traeth y Mwnt
tags.note: No dogs allowed on any part of the beach from 1st May to 30th September.
